title: CS-GO VERSION
description:
About game
This version is based on the CS 1.6 version but is totally different from this in terms of changes made. About CSGO we can say that it is the latest version of CS published by Valve but still has not managed to cross the classic CS 1.6. CSGO comes with changes in graphics but also with a complex trading system for weapons and equipment in the game. The game was released in 2015 and just like CS 1.6 is a tactical shooter video game. Bring some weapons and extra equipment. In addition to these changes, CSGO also brings some ways to play casual & competitive, arms race, demolition and deathmatch. A Counter-Strike with skins, modified sounds and patterns. The skin is HD quality and looks great. This edition is based on CS: GO. Radio, hostage models, hands and weapons models,
